  uid=2_25 heading "SUNDROPS MEZZO PROGRAM" level="2"
  uid=2_26 StaticText "7th to 9th Grade. The Sundrops Adolescent Erdkinder Program addresses the unique needs of the middle schooler. The Edkinder program is a carefully constructed environment allowing for living on the land and learning self-sufficiency. The small community of the farm requires all students to play a role, and often to step out of their comfort zone to realize their potential and success on the farm. See the video tour below."
